attributes.name: Qwen: Qwen2.5 VL 32B Instruct
attributes.description: Qwen2.5-VL-32B is a multimodal vision-language model fine-tuned through reinforcement learning for enhanced mathematical reasoning, structured outputs, and visual problem-solving capabilities. It excels at visual analysis tasks, including object recognition, textual interpretation within images, and precise event localization in extended videos. Qwen2.5-VL-32B demonstrates state-of-the-art performance across multimodal benchmarks such as MMMU, MathVista, and VideoMME, while maintaining strong reasoning and clarity in text-based tasks like MMLU, mathematical problem-solving, and code generation.
